SEC. 106. For an additional amount for the program 

established under section 7522 of the Food, Conservation, 

and Energy Act of 2008 (7 U.S.C. 5936), to prevent, pre-

pare  for,  and  respond  to  coronavirus,  $20,000,000:  Pro-

vided,  That  such  amount  is  designated  by  the  Congress 

