SEC.  107.  Section  11004  in  title  I  of  division  B  of 

the  Coronavirus  Aid,  Relief,  and  Economic  Security  Act 

(Public  Law  116136)  is  amended  by  inserting  after  the 

fourth  proviso  the  following:  Provided  further,  That  the 

condition set forth in section 9003(f) of the Farm Security 

and Rural Investment Act of 2002 shall apply with respect 

to all construction, alteration, or repair work carried out, 

in whole or in part, with funds made available by this sec-

tion::  Provided,  That  amounts  repurposed  pursuant  to 

the  amendments  made  pursuant  to  this  section  are  des-

ignated  by  the  Congress  as  being  for  an  emergency  re-

quirement pursuant to section 251(b)(2)(A)(i) of the Bal-

anced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985. 

