GENERAL PROVISIONSTHIS TITLE 

SEC.  401.  Funds  appropriated  in  this  title  may  be 

made  available  to  restore  amounts,  either  directly  or 

through  reimbursement,  for  obligations  incurred  for  the 

same  purposes  to  prevent,  prepare  for,  and  respond  to 

coronavirus  prior  to  the  date  of  enactment  of  this  Act. 

