emergency  telehealth  funding  has  been  obligated,  on  the 

status of approved applications, pending applications, and 

rejected  applications  for  such  funding,  and  on  rec-

ommendations  to  improve  the  transparency  and  fairness 

of  distribution  of  such  funding:  Provided  further,  That 

such  amount  is  designated  by  the  Congress  as  being  for 

an 

emergency 

requirement 

pursuant 

to 

section 

251(b)(2)(A)(i)  of  the  Balanced  Budget  and  Emergency 

Deficit Control Act of 1985. 

