SEC. 902. Funds appropriated to the Architect of the 

Capitol  in  this  Act  also  may  be  used  to  restore  amounts, 

either  directly  or  through  reimbursement,  for  obligations 

incurred by the Architect to prevent, prepare for, and re-

spond to Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID19) prior to 

the  date  of  enactment  of  this  Act.  Funds  used  to  restore 

amounts  to  other  Architect  of  the  Capitol  accounts  shall 

assume the original period of availability of such accounts. 

