this heading to its own charter members with exper-

tise  in  housing  counseling,  subject  to  a  certification 

by the NRC that the procedures for selection do not 

consist  of  any  procedures  or  activities  that  could  be 

construed  as  an  unacceptable  conflict  of  interest  or 

have the appearance of impropriety. 

