SEC. 100. SHORT TITLE. 

This  division  may  be  cited  as  the  Pandemic  Edu-

cation Response Act. 

TITLE IHIGHER EDUCATION 

PROVISIONS 

SEC. 101. DEFINITIONS. 

In this title: 

(1) AWARD YEAR.The term award year has 

the  meaning  given  the  term  in  section  481(a)  of  the 

Higher Education Act of 1965 (20 U.S.C. 1088(a)). 

(2)  AUTHORIZING COMMITTEES.The 

term 

authorizing committees has the meaning given the 

term  in  section  103  of  the  Higher  Education  Act  of 

1965 (20 U.S.C. 1003). 

(3)  FAFSA.The  term  FAFSA  means  an 

application  under  section  483  of  the  Higher  Edu-

cation  Act  of  1965  (20  U.S.C.  1090)  for  Federal 

student financial aid. 

