(c)  FEDERAL PERKINS LOANS.Notwithstanding 

section  465  of  the  Higher  Education  Act  of  1965  (20 

U.S.C.  1087ee),  the  Secretary  shall  waive  the  require-

ments  of  such  section  in  regard  to  full-time  service  and 

shall consider an incomplete year of service of a borrower 

as fulfilling the requirement for a complete year of service 

under  such  section,  if  the  service  was  interrupted  due  to 

a qualifying emergency.. 

