of  higher  education  that  does  not  meet  the  re-

quirements  of  subparagraph  (A)  shall  cease  of-

fering  distance  education  programs  until  such 

time  that  such  institution  demonstrates  to  the 

Secretary  that  the  institution  and  each  of  its 

applicable  programs  meet  the  requirements  of 

subparagraph (A). 

