of 1965 (20 U.S.C. 1070 et seq.): 

(A) The Federal Pell Grant program under 

section 401 of such Act (20 U.S.C. 1070a). 

(B)  The  Federal  Supplemental  Edu-

cational Opportunity Grant program under sub-

part  3  of  part  A  of  such  title  IV  (20  U.S.C. 

1070b). 

