(5)  APPROVAL OF TEACH-OUT AGREEMENTS. 

In  approving  a  teach-out  agreement,  the  accrediting 

agency  or  association  shall  determine  a  timeline  for 

an interim teach-out agreement and a final teach-out 

agreement  that  provides  for  the  equitable  treatment 

of students and ensures 

