Health and Human Services) during 

(i)  the  repayment  period  of  such 

loan; 

(ii)  any  period  excluded  from  the  re-

payment period of such loan (including any 

period of deferment or forbearance); 

(iii)  any  period  in  which  the  bor-

rower  of  such  loan  is  in  a  grace  period;  or 

(iv) any period in which the borrower 

of such loan is in default on such loan. 

