SEC. 136. EFFECTIVE DATE. 

Except  as  otherwise  provided,  this  part,  and  the 

amendments made by this part, shall take effect as if en-

acted  as  part  of  the  Coronavirus  Aid,  Relief,  and  Eco-

nomic Security Act (Public Law 116136). 

