(c) PARENT.Section 110(a)(1) is amended by add-

ing at the end the following: 

(C)  PARENT.In  lieu  of  the  definition  in 

section  101(7),  the  term  parent,  with  respect 

to an employee, means any of the following: 

(i)  A  biological,  foster,  or  adoptive 

parent of the employee. 

(ii) A stepparent of the employee. 

(iii) A parent-in-law of the employee. 

(iv)  A  parent  of  a  domestic  partner 

of the employee. 

(v)  A  legal  guardian  or  other  person 

who  stood  in  loco  parentis  to  an  employee 

when the employee was a child.. 

