(ii)  COMMITTED RELATIONSHIP DE-

FINED.The term committed relationship 

means a relationship between 2 individuals, 

each  at  least  18  years  of  age,  in  which 

each  individual  is  the  other  individuals 

sole  domestic  partner  and  both  individuals 

share  responsibility  for  a  significant  meas-

ure  of  each  others  common  welfare.  The 

term  includes  any  such  relationship  be-

tween  2  individuals  that  is  granted  legal 

recognition  by  a  State  or  political  subdivi-

sion of a State as a marriage or analogous 

relationship,  including  a  civil  union  or  do-

mestic partnership.. 

