SEC. 121. REFERENCES. 

Except  as  otherwise  expressly  provided,  whenever  in 

this subtitle an amendment or repeal is expressed in terms 

of an amendment to, or repeal of, a section or other provi-

sion,  the  reference  shall  be  considered  to  be  made  to  a 

section  or  other  provision  of  division  E  of  the  Families 

First  Coronavirus  Response  Act  (Public  Law  116127). 

