HEALTH EMERGENCY.The  term  qualifying  need 

related  to  a  public  health  emergency  has  the  mean-

ing  given  such  term  in  section  110(a)(2)(A)  of  the 

Family  and  Medical  Leave  Act  of  1993  (29  U.S.C. 

2620(a)(2)(A)).. 

