(B) was 

(i)  at  any  time  during  the  period  be-

ginning  on  January  27,  2020,  and  ending 

on  February  27,  2022,  diagnosed  with 

COVID19; or 

(ii)  at  any  time  during  the  period  de-

scribed  in  subparagraph  (A),  ordered  not 

to  return  to  work  by  the  employees  em-

ployer  or  by  a  local,  State,  or  Federal 

agency  because  of  exposure,  or  the  risk  of 

