38,  United  States  Code)  employed  in  the  Fed-

eral service at anytime during the period begin-

ning  on  January  27,  2020,  and  ending  on  Jan-

uary 30, 2022 

(i)  who  carried  out  duties  requiring 

contact with patients, members of the pub-

lic, or co-workers; or 

(ii)  whose  duties  include  a  risk  of  ex-

