SEC.  502.  JOB  CORPS  RESPONSE  TO  THE  COVID19  NA-

TIONAL EMERGENCY. 

In  order  to  provide  for  the  successful  continuity  of 

services and enrollment periods during the COVID19 na-

tional  emergency,  additional  flexibility  shall  be  provided 

for  Job  Corps  operators,  providers  of  eligible  activities, 

and practitioners, including the following: 

(1)  ELIGIBILITY.Notwithstanding  the  age  re-

quirements  for  enrollment  under  section  144(a)(1) 

of  the  Workforce  Innovation  and  Opportunity  Act 

(29  U.S.C.  3194(a)(1)),  an  individual  seeking  to  en-

roll  in  Job  Corps  and  who  turns  25  during  the 

