Human  Services  and  Community  Supports  Act,  the 

Secretary  shall  develop  and  issue  final  regulations 

establishing  uniform  standards  for  the  tracking  and 

reporting of child fatalities and near-fatalities result-

ing  from  maltreatment.  As  a  condition  on  eligibility 

for receipt of funds under section 106, the standards 

established  under  this  paragraph  shall  be  used  by 

States  for  the  tracking  and  reporting  of  such  fatali-

ties under subsection (d) of such section. 

