(I)  any  changes  to  State  law  or 

regulations,  relating  to  the  prevention 

of  child  abuse  and  neglect  that  may 

affect the eligibility of the State under 

this section; or 

(II)  any  changes  in  the  States 

activities, 

strategies,  or  programs 

under this section.. 

