SEC. 121. PURPOSE AND AUTHORITY. 

Section  201  of  the  Child  Abuse  Prevention  and 

Treatment  Act  (42  U.S.C.  5116)  is  amended  to  read  as 

follows: 

SEC. 201. PURPOSE AND AUTHORITY. 

(a) PURPOSE.It is the purpose of this title 

