SEC. 128. DEFINITIONS. 

Section  208  of  the  Child  Abuse  Prevention  and 

Treatment Act (42 U.S.C. 5116h) is amended 

(1)  by  redesignating  paragraphs  (1)  and  (2)  as 

paragraphs  (2)  and  (1),  respectively,  and  transfer-

