required  to  be  repaid  by  a  lender  unless 

the  lender  is  found  guilty  of  an  act  of 

fraud 

in  connection  with  the  covered 

loan.. 

SEC.  216.  DUPLICATION  REQUIREMENTS  FOR  ECONOMIC 

INJURY DISASTER LOAN RECIPIENTS. 

Section  7(a)(36)(Q)  of  the  Small  Business  Act  (15 

U.S.C. 636(a)(36)(Q)) is amended by striking during the 

period beginning on January 31, 2020, and ending on the 

date on which covered loans are made available. 

SEC.  217.  REAPPLICATION  FOR  AND  MODIFICATION  TO 

