ument  an  economic  loss  caused  by  the  closure 

of  the  United  States  and  Canadian  border  that 

restricted  the  ability  of  American  customers  to 

access the location of the covered entity. 

(G)  SMALL BUSINESS CONCERN.The 

term  small  business  concern  has  the  meaning 

