after  the  initial  receipt  by  the  Administrator  of 

an  application  under  this  subsection,  the  Ad-

ministrator  shall  provide  the  applicant  with  a 

written  report  detailing  the  status  of  the  appli-

cation  and  any  requirements  remaining  for 

completion of the application. 

