(9)  PROGRAM PARTICIPANT.The  term  Pro-

gram participant means a micro-SBIC that received 

a  seed  investment  under  the  Seed  Investment  Pro-

gram established by section 399C. 

(10)  SCALE-UP SMALL BUSINESS.The  term 

