concern that 

(A)  is  domestically  domiciled  within  the 

United States; 

(B)  during  the  3-year  period  preceding 

the date of application, has not generated earn-

ings  before  interest,  tax,  depreciation,  and  am-

ortization in excess of $3,000,000; 

(C)  produces  a  majority  of  its  goods  or 

provides a majority of its services in the United 

States; and 

(D)  does  not  move  production  or  employ-

ment outside the United States. 

