requested  by  a  lender  under  subparagraph  (B),  the 

Administrator  shall  exercise  the  authority  to  pur-

chase  the  loan  so  that  the  borrower  may  receive  full 

payment  deferment  relief  (including  payment  of 

principal and interest) or an additional deferment as 

described under subparagraph (B).. 

