ment company under subparagraph (A) shall be 

in  an  amount  equal  to  1.5  percent  of  the  net 

debenture  proceeds  for  which  the  development 

company  does  not  collect  a  processing  fee  pur-

suant to paragraph (1)(B). 

SEC. 608. EXTENSION OF PARTICIPATION IN 8(A) PROGRAM. 

(a)  IN GENERAL.The  Administrator  shall  ensure 

that a small business concern participating in the program 

established  under  section  8(a)  of  the  Small  Business  Act 

on  or  before  March  13,  2020,  may  elect  to  extend  such 

participation by a period of 1 year, regardless of whether 

such  concern  previously  elected  to  suspend  participation 

in  such  program  pursuant  to  guidance  of  the  Adminis-

trator. 

(b)  EMERGENCY RULEMAKING AUTHORITY.Not 

later than 15 days after the date of enactment of this sec-

tion, the Administrator shall issue regulations to carry out 

