Railroad Retirement Board, and 

(III)  in  the  case  of  a  specified 

veterans  beneficiary,  the  Secretary  of 

Veterans  Affairs 

(in 

coordination 

with,  and  with  the  assistance  of,  the 

Commissioner of Social Security if ap-

propriate). 

