Sec. 6428A. Additional recovery rebates to individuals.. 

(d)  CERTAIN REQUIREMENTS RELATED TO RECOV-

ERY REBATES AND ADDITIONAL RECOVERY REBATES. 

(1)  SIGNATURES ON CHECKS AND NOTICES, 

ETC.,  BY THE DEPARTMENT OF THE TREASURY. 

