to  the  loss  (if  any)  to  that  possession  by  reason  of 

the  application  of  the  provisions  of  this  section 

(other  than  this  subsection)  with  respect  to  section 

32  of  the  Internal  Revenue  Code  of  1986.  Such 

amounts shall be determined by the Secretary of the 

