with  respect  to  such  bases)  shall  be  reduced  to 

zero, and 

(B)  subparagraphs  (A)  and  (B)  of  para-

graph  (2)  shall  each  be  applied  by  substituting 

15-plan-year  period  for  7-plan-year  period.. 

