(1)  shall  be  made  at  such  time  and  in  such  manner 

as prescribed by the Secretary of the Treasury. Such 

election, once made with respect to a plan year, shall 

apply  to  all  subsequent  plan  years  unless  revoked 

with  the  consent  of  the  Secretary  of  the  Treasury. 

