(c)  COORDINATION WITH FUNDING RULES.Ex-

cept as otherwise provided in this title, sections 302, 304, 

and 305 shall not apply to a composite plan. 

(d) TREATMENT OF A COMPOSITE PLAN.For pur-

poses  of  this  Act  (other  than  sections  302  and  4245),  a 

composite plan shall be treated as if it were a defined ben-

efit plan unless a different treatment is provided for under 

applicable law. 

