LIMIT APPLIES.Subsection  (a)  shall  not  apply  in  con-

nection  with  a  plan  amendment  if  and  to  the  extent  that 

contributions  to  the  composite  plan  would  not  be  deduct-

ible  for  the  plan  year  under  section  404(a)(1)(E)  of  the 

Internal Revenue Code of 1986 if the plan amendment is 

not adopted. 

