posite  plan  has 

certified  under 

section 

305(b)(3)  that  such  defined  benefit  plan  is  or 

will  be  in  critical  status  for  the  plan  year  in 

which  such  agreement  would  take  effect  or  for 

any of the succeeding 5 plan years; and 

(B)  unless  the  agreement  requires  each 

employer  who  is  a  party  to  such  agreement,  in-

cluding employers whose employees are not par-

ticipants in the legacy plan, to provide contribu-

tions  to  the  legacy  plan  with  respect  to  such 

