entered  into  after  the  date  of  enactment  of  the  Giv-

ing  Retirement  Options  to  Workers  Act  of  2020, 

ceases to have an obligation to contribute to a multi-

employer  defined  benefit  plan,  no  employees  em-

ployed by the employer may accrue or otherwise earn 

