a  plan  year  is  the  rate  in  effect  for  the 

plan  year  of  the  legacy  plan  that  com-

mences  on  or  after  180  days  before  the 

earlier of 

(I)  the  effective  date  of  the  col-

lective bargaining agreement pursuant 

to  which  the  employer  contributes  to 

the legacy plan; or 

(II)  5  years  after  the  last  plan 

year for which the transition contribu-

