effective date of the amendment, 

(B)  apply  with  respect  to  all  participants 

in  the  multiemployer  plan  for  whom  contribu-

tions  are  made  to  the  multiemployer  plan  on  or 

after the effective date of the amendment, 

(C)  specify  that  the  effective  date  of  the 

amendment is 

