hundred  twentieth  day  of  each  plan  year  of  a  com-

posite  plan,  the  plan  actuary  of  the  composite  plan 

shall  certify  to  the  Secretary,  the  Secretary  of 

Labor, and the plan sponsor the plans current fund-

