SEC. 440. LIMITATION ON INCREASING BENEFITS. 

(a) LEVEL OF CURRENT FUNDED RATIOS.Except 

as  provided  in  subsections  (c),  (d),  and  (e),  no  plan 

amendment  increasing  benefits  or  establishing  new  bene-

fits  under  a  composite  plan  may  be  adopted  for  a  plan 

year unless 

