similar to those provided in section 625.6 of title 20, 

Code  of  Federal  Regulations,  for  weeks  ending  be-

fore the effective date specified in paragraph (1), an 

individual  who  received  Pandemic  Unemployment 

Assistance  from  such  State  for  any  such  week  shall 

not  be  considered  ineligible  for  such  assistance  for 

such week solely by reason of failure to submit a re-

certification  described  in  subsection  (c)(4)  of  such 

section. 

