time  that  a  State  has  failed  to  take  reasonable 

actions  under  a  corrective  action  plan  to  ad-

dress  a  claims  backlog,  the  State  shall  collabo-

rate with the Secretary to develop a subsequent 

corrective action plan to achieve clearly defined, 

targeted outcomes. 

