(D)  to  provide  prepaid  grocery  cards  to  an 

eligible  family  (as  defined  in  section  511(k)(2) 

of  such  Act)  for  the  purpose  of  enabling  the 

family to meet the emergency needs of the fam-

ily. 

(b)  VIRTUAL HOME VISIT DEFINED.In  subsection 

(a),  the  term  virtual  home  visit  means  a  visit  that  is 

conducted  solely  by  the  use  of  electronic  information  and 

telecommunications technologies. 

