PRIATIONS.For  fiscal  year  2021,  out  of  any  money  in 

the  Treasury  of  the  United  States  not  otherwise  appro-

priated,  there  are  authorized  to  be  appropriated  to  the 

Secretary  of  Health  and  Human  Services  $1,000,000  to 

carry out this section. 

