such facility, resides in such portion of such fa-

cility) 

(i) a specification of when and where 

such resident will be transferred (or moved 

within such facility); 

(ii)  an  explanation  that,  in  lieu  of 

such  transfer  or  move,  such  resident  may 

arrange  for  transfer  to  such  other  setting 

(including  a  home)  selected  by  the  resi-

dent; and 

