(6)  DEFINITION.For  purposes  of  this  sub-

section,  the  term  eligible  individual  means  an  indi-

vidual  who,  during  the  30-day  period  ending  on  the 

first  day  on  which  such  individual  is  a  resident  of  a 

COVID19  treatment  center  (on  or  after  the  date 

such  center  is  so  designated),  was  furnished  a  test 

for COVID19 that came back positive. 

