clear  and  understandable  to  the  average  participant 

or beneficiary) 

(A)  of  whether  such  plan  will  waive,  dur-

ing  such  period  with  respect  to  such  a  partici-

pant  or  beneficiary,  any  time  restrictions  under 

such  plan  on  any  authorized  refills  for  such 

drugs  to  enable  such  refills  in  advance  of  when 

such  refills  would  otherwise  have  been  per-

mitted under such plan; and 

(B)  in  the  case  that  such  plan  will  waive 

such  restrictions  during  such  period  with  re-

spect  to  such  a  participant  or  beneficiary,  that 

