SEC. 306. SOONER COVERAGE OF TESTING FOR COVID19. 

Section  6001(a)  of  division  F  of  the  Families  First 

Coronavirus  Response  Act  (42  U.S.C.  1320b5  note)  is 

amended by striking beginning on or after and inserting 

