the Families First Coronavirus Response Act (Public 

Law  116127)  to  ensure  that  individuals  enrolled  in 

individual  or  group  health  insurance  coverage  or 

group  health  plans  (including  grandfathered  health 

plans  (as  defined  in  section  1251(e)  of  the  Patient 

