(d) PUBLIC REPORT.Not later than 60 days after 

the date of the enactment of this subsection, the Secretary 

of Health and Human Services shall publish on the Inter-

net  website  of  the  Department  of  Health  and  Human 

Services  a  report  on  cash  prices  for  items  and  services 

