with  the  publication  requirement  under  such  sub-

section; 

(2)  the  average  cash  price  for  each  item  and 

service  described  in  section  6001(a)  of  division  F  of 

the Families First Coronavirus Response Act that is 

published under such subsection; 

(3) with respect to each such item and service, 

a comparison of such average cash price to the reim-

bursement  rate  under  the  Medicare  program  under 

title  XVIII  of  the  Social  Security  Act  (42  U.S.C. 

1395 et seq.); and 

(4)  any  cash  prices  published  under  such  sub-

section  that  substantially  exceed  the  average  cash 

price  for  each  such  item  or  service  and  the  name  of 

each provider that charges such prices.. 

