(2)  APPLICABLE PERIOD.For  purposes  of 

this  section,  the  applicable  period  is  the  period 

that 

(A)  begins  on  the  date  of  the  enactment 

of this subsection, and 

(B) ends 60 days after the last day of the 

emergency 

period 

described 

in 

