Security Act of 1974. 

(4)  QUALIFIED HEALTH PLAN.The  term 

qualified  health  plan  has  the  meaning  given  such 

term in section 1301(a)(1) of the Patient Protection 

and Affordable Care Act. 

(5)  STATE.The  term  State  includes  the 

District  of  Columbia,  the  Commonwealth  of  Puerto 

Rico,  the  Virgin  Islands,  Guam,  American  Samoa, 

