spect to an individual 

(A)  regular  compensation  and  extended 

compensation  (as  such  terms  are  defined  by 

section  205  of  the  Federal-State  Extended  Un-

employment Compensation Act of 1970); 

(B)  unemployment  compensation  (as  de-

