compensation  under  section  2107  of 

the 

CARES Act; 

(E) unemployment benefits under the Rail-

road Unemployment Insurance Act; and 

(F) trade adjustment assistance under title 

II of the Trade Act of 1974; 

for  which  such  individual  is  eligible  for  any  week 

during the period described in subsection (a)(2). 

