CoV2 in the United States; 

(B)  to  ensure  that  any  reduction  in  social 

distancing efforts, when determined appropriate 

by  public  health  officials,  can  be  undertaken  in 

a  manner  that  optimizes  the  health  and  safety 

of  the  people  of  the  United  States,  and  reduces 

