(d)  APPROPRIATE CONGRESSIONAL COMMITTEES. 

In this section, the term appropriate congressional com-

mittees means 

(1)  the  Committee  on  Appropriations  and  the 

Committee  on  Energy  and  Commerce  of  the  House 

of Representatives; and 

(2)  the  Committee  on  Appropriations  and  the 

Committee  on  Health,  Education,  Labor  and  Pen-

sions and of the Senate. 

