SEC.  549.  PILOT  PROGRAM  TO  IMPROVE  LABORATORY  IN-

FRASTRUCTURE. 

(a) IN GENERAL.The Secretary shall award grants 

to  States  and  political  subdivisions  of  States  to  support 

the  improvement,  renovation,  or  modernization  of  infra-

structure at clinical laboratories (as defined in section 353 

of  the  Public  Health  Service  Act  (42  U.S.C.  263a))  that 

will help to improve SARSCoV2 and COVID19 testing 

and  response  activities,  including  the  expansion  and  en-

hancement of testing capacity at such laboratories. 

(b) AUTHORIZATION OF APPROPRIATIONS.To carry 

out  this  section,  there  is  authorized  to  be  appropriated 

$1,000,000,000 to remain available until expended. 

