SEC.  577.  ADDITIONAL  REPORTING  TO  CONGRESS  ON  THE 

RACE  AND  ETHNICITY  RATES  OF  COVID19 

TESTING,  HOSPITALIZATIONS,  AND  MORTALI-

TIES. 

(a)  IN GENERAL.Not  later  than  30  days  after  the 

date  of  enactment  of  this  Act,  the  Secretary  shall  submit 

