tality 

rates 

associated 

with 

COVID19, 

disaggregated  by  race,  ethnicity,  age,  sex,  gender, 

geographic  region,  and  other  relevant  factors  as  de-

termined by the Secretary; 

(2)  including  an  analysis  of  any  variances  of 

testing,  positive  diagnoses,  hospitalizations,  and 

deaths by demographic characteristics; and 

