SEC.  581.  TECHNICAL  CORRECTIONS  TO  AMENDMENTS 

MADE BY CARES ACT. 

(a) The amendments made by this section shall take 

effect  as  if  included  in  the  enactment  of  the  CARES  Act 

(Public Law 116136). 

(b)  Section  3112  of  division  A  of  the  CARES  Act 

(Public Law 116136) is amended 

(1)  in  subsection  (a)(2)(A),  by  striking  the 

comma before or a permanent; 

(2)  in  subsection  (d)(1),  by  striking  and  sub-

paragraphs (A) and (B) and inserting as subpara-

graphs (A) and (B); and 

(3)  in  subsection  (e),  by  striking  Drug,  Cos-

metic Act and inserting Drug, and Cosmetic Act. 

