(2)  REVIEW AND PAYMENT.The  Secretary 

shall 

(A)  review  applications  and  make  awards 

of  reimbursement  under  this  section  on  a  quar-

terly basis; and 

(B)  award  the  reimbursements  under  this 

section for a quarter not later than 14 calendar 

days  after  the  close  of  the  quarter,  except  that 

the  Secretary  shall  award  the  reimbursements 

under this section for the quarters beginning on 

January 1 and April 1, 2020, not later than 14 

calendar  days  after  the  date  of  enactment  of 

this Act. 

