(e) LOST REVENUES. 

(1) IN GENERAL.Subject to subsection (h)(1), 

for  purposes  of  subsection  (c)(1)(A)(ii),  the  lost  rev-

enues  of  an  eligible  health  care  provider,  with  re-

spect to the calendar quarter involved, shall be equal 

to 

