the  corresponding  quarter  in  2019  minus  net 

patient  revenue  of  the  provider  for  such  quar-

ter; less 

(B)  the  savings  of  the  provider  during  the 

calendar  quarter  involved  attributable  to  fore-

gone  wages,  payroll  taxes,  and  benefits  of  per-

sonnel  who  were  furloughed  or  laid  off  by  the 

provider during that quarter. 

