dian Tribes. 

(c)  USE OF FUNDS.An  eligible  entity  receiving  a 

grant  under  this  section  shall  use  funds  received  through 

the grant 

(1)  to  advance  quality  of  care  in  response  to 

COVID19,  with  particular  emphasis  on  rural  and 

underserved areas and populations; 

(2)  to  protect  medical  personnel  and  first  re-

sponders through sharing real-time learning through 

virtual communities of practice; 

(3)  to  improve  patient  outcomes  for  conditions 

affected or exacerbated by COVID19, including im-

provement  of  care  for  patients  with  complex  chronic 

conditions; and 

