(f)  NO DUPLICATIVE ASSISTANCE LIMITATION. 

The Secretary may not provide, and a State, local, Tribal, 

or  territorial  health  department,  or  employer  of  essential 

workers may not accept, assistance under this section for 

containment  and  mitigation  of  COVID19  transmission 

