ceives  assistance  from  other  sources  for  such  pur-

poses; or 

(2)  other  sources  are  obligated  to  provide  as-

sistance  to  such  health  department  or  employer  for 

such purposes. 

(g)  TECHNICAL ASSISTANCE.In  carrying  out  the 

program  under  this  section,  the  Secretary  shall  provide 

technical  assistance  to  State,  local,  Tribal,  or  territorial 

health departments. 

