the  COVID19  pandemic  and  ending  90  days  after 

the last day of such emergency period. 

SEC.  107.  PROVISION  OF  DEPARTMENT  OF  VETERANS  AF-

FAIRS  HOSPITAL  CARE  AND  MEDICAL  SERV-

