HEALTH  CARE  COVERAGE  BY  REASON  OF  A 

COVERED PUBLIC HEALTH EMERGENCY. 

(a)  IN GENERAL.During  the  12-month  period  be-

ginning  on  the  date  on  which  a  covered  veteran  applies 

for  hospital  care  or  medical  services  under  this  section, 

the  Secretary  of  Veterans  Affairs  shall  consider  the  cov-

ered  veteran  to  be  unable  to  defray  the  expenses  of  nec-

