(1)  REIMBURSEMENT OF 100 PERCENT OF 

COSTS.In  providing  support  under  the  regulations 

required  by  subsection  (a),  the  Commission  shall  re-

imburse 100 percent of the costs associated with the 

equipment described in subsection (c), advanced tele-

