vider, a household in which 

(A)  at  least  one  member  of  the  household 

meets the qualifications in subsection (a) or (b) 

of  section  54.409  of  title  47,  Code  of  Federal 

Regulations (or any successor regulation); 

(B)  at  least  one  member  of  the  household 

has  applied  for  and  been  approved  to  receive 

