(1)  ADVANCED TELECOMMUNICATIONS SERV-

ICE.The  term  advanced  telecommunications  serv-

ice  means  a  service  that  provides  advanced  tele-

communications capability (as defined in section 706 

of  the  Telecommunications  Act  of  1996  (47  U.S.C. 

1302)). 

