facility, or to individuals inside the confinement 

facility,  where  the  incarcerated  person  is  being 

held,  regardless  of  the  technology  used  to  de-

liver the service. 

(F)  CONSUMER.The  term  consumer 

means  the  party  paying  a  provider  of  confine-

ment facility communications services. 

(G)  DEBIT CALLING.The  term  debit 

calling  means  a  presubscription  or  comparable 

