graph (2), the Secretary shall require a grant recipi-

ent  under  this  section  to  provide  matching  non-Fed-

eral  funds  in  an  amount  equal  to  the  amount  of  a 

grant. 

(2)  EXCEPTION.The  Secretary  shall  not  re-

