payments  under  subsection  (a)  not  later  than  60  days 

after the date of the enactment of this section. 

(e)  FUNDING.There  is  appropriated,  out  of  any 

funds in the Treasury not otherwise appropriated, to carry 

out this section $1,250,000,000, to remain available until 

expended. 

