of  less  than  5  million  pounds,  as  determined  in 

accordance  with  subsection  (c)  of  such  section 

1405. 

(2)  LIMITATION ON ELIGIBILITY.An  eligible 

dairy  operation  shall  only  be  eligible  for  payments 

under  this  section  during  a  calendar  year  in  which 

such eligible dairy operation is enrolled in dairy mar-

gin coverage (as defined in section 1401 of the Agri-

cultural Act of 2014 (7 U.S.C. 9051)). 

