(2) PAYMENTS. 

(A) RENTAL RATE.Except as provided in 

paragraph  (4)(B)(ii),  the  annual  rental  rate  for 

a  payment  under  a  contract  described  in  sub-

section (b) shall be $70 per acre. 

(B)  ADVANCE PAYMENT.At  the  request 

of  the  owner  and  (if  applicable)  the  operator  of 

the  eligible  land,  the  Secretary  shall  make  all 

rental  payments  under  a  contract  entered  into 

under  this  section  within  30  days  of  entering 

into such contract. 

(C)  COST SHARE PAYMENTS.A  contract 

described  in  subsection  (b)  shall  provide  that, 

during  the  term  of  the  contract,  the  Secretary 

shall  pay,  of  the  actual  cost  of  establishment  of 

the  conserving  use  cover  crop  under  paragraph 

(1)(B)(i), not more than $30 per acre. 

(3) TERM. 

