igible  land  enrolled  in  the  pilot  program 

under  this  section  may  terminate  a  con-

tract described in subsection (b) before the 

end  of  the  term  described  in  subparagraph 

(A) if the owner and (if applicable) the op-

erator  pay  to  the  Secretary  an  amount 

equal to the amount of rental payments re-

ceived under the contract. 

