DIVISION OCOVID19 HERO 

ACT 

SEC. 1. SHORT TITLE. 

This division may be cited as the COVID19 Hous-

ing, Economic Relief, and Oversight Act or the COVID 

19 HERO Act. 
TITLE  IPROVIDING  MEDICAL 
EQUIPMENT  FOR  FIRST  RE-
SPONDERS  AND  ESSENTIAL 
WORKERS 

SEC.  101.  COVID19  EMERGENCY  MEDICAL  SUPPLIES  EN-

HANCEMENT. 

(a) DETERMINATION ON EMERGENCY SUPPLIES AND 

RELATIONSHIP TO STATE AND LOCAL EFFORTS. 

(1) DETERMINATION.For the purposes of sec-

tion 101 of the Defense Production Act of 1950 (50 

U.S.C.  4511),  the  following  materials  shall  be 

deemed  to  be  scarce  and  critical  materials  essential 

to  the  national  defense  and  otherwise  meet  the  re-

quirements  of  section  101(b)  of  such  Act  during  the 

COVID19 emergency period: 

(A)  Diagnostic  tests,  including  serological 

tests,  for  COVID19  and  the  reagents  and 

other  materials  necessary  for  producing  or  con-

ducting such tests. 

