for  COVID19)  and  any  materials  necessary  to 

produce  or  use  such  pharmaceuticals  or  medi-

cines  (including  self-injection  syringes  or  other 

delivery systems). 

(E)  Any  other  medical  equipment  or  sup-

plies determined by the Secretary of Health and 

Human  Services  or  the  Secretary  of  Homeland 

Security  to  be  scarce  and  critical  materials  es-

sential  to  the  national  defense  for  purposes  of 

