(1) SENSE OF CONGRESS.The Congress 

(A)  appreciates  the  willingness  of  private 

companies  not  traditionally  involved  in  pro-

ducing  items  for  the  health  sector  to  volunteer 

to  use  their  expertise  and  supply  chains  to 

produce  essential  medical  supplies  and  equip-

ment; 

(B)  encourages  other  manufacturers  to  re-

view  their  existing  capacity  and  to  develop  ca-

pacity  to  produce  essential  medical  supplies, 

