this paragraph shall include 

(i)  an  assessment  of  the  needs  for 

medical supplies or equipment necessary to 

address  the  needs  of  the  population  of  the 

United States infected by the virus SARS 

CoV2  that  causes  COVID19  and  to  pre-

vent  an 

increase 

in  the 

incidence  of 

COVID19  throughout  the  United  States, 

including  diagnostic  tests,  serological  tests, 

