(e) 3-YEAR AVAILABILITY. 

(1)  IN GENERAL.Each  recipient  of  amounts 

made available pursuant to subsection (b) shall 

(A) expend not less than 60 percent of the 

grant  amounts  within  2  years  of  the  date  on 

which  the  funds  became  available  to  the  recipi-

ent for obligation; and 

(B)  expend  100  percent  of  the  grant 

amounts  within  3  years  of  the  date  on  which 

the  funds  became  available  to  the  recipient  for 

obligation. 

