ance  programs,  shall  provide  reports  to  the 

Congress, and make such reports publicly avail-

able,  not  less  frequently  than  quarterly  regard-

ing  the  impact  of  COVID19  pandemic  on  the 

such  enterprises  and  programs  ability  to  meet 

their  charter  requirements,  civil  rights  respon-

sibilities,  mandates  under  the  CARES  Act 

