(b)  RENEWAL

OF

CONTINUUM

OF

CARE 

PROJECTS. 

(1)  IN GENERAL.In  allocating  and  awarding 

amounts  provided  for  the  Continuum  of  Care  pro-

gram  under  subtitle  C  of  title  IV  of  the  McKinney- 

Vento Homeless Assistance Act (42 U.S.C. 11381 et 

