riod. 

 (d) SUMMARY OF RIGHTS.Not later than 60 days 

after  the  date  of  enactment  of  this  section,  the  Director 

of  the  Bureau  shall  update  the  model  summary  of  rights 

under  section  609(c)(1)  to  include  a  description  of  the 

right of a consumer to 

 (1)  request  the  deletion  of  adverse  items  of 

information under subsection (e); and 

 (2)  request  a  consumer  report  or  score,  with-

out charge to the consumer, under subsection (f). 

