 (B)  not  later  than  15  minutes  if  the  re-

quest is made online. 

 (3)  ADDITIONAL REPORTS.A  file  disclosure 

provided under paragraph (1) shall be in addition to 

any disclosure requested by the consumer under sec-

tion 612(a). 

 (4)  PROHIBITION.A  consumer  reporting 

agency  that  receives  a  request  under  paragraph  (1) 

may  not  request  or  require  any  documentation  from 

the  consumer  that  demonstrates  that  the  consumer 

was  impacted  by  the  coronavirus  disease  (COVID 

19)  outbreak  or  a  major  disaster  (except  to  verify 

