(A)  the  total  amount  of  each  private  edu-

cation loan of the borrower; or 

(B)  $10,000,  reduced  by  the  aggregate 

amount  of  all  payments  made  by  the  Secretary 

of  the  Treasury  with  respect  to  such  borrower 

