gas,  telecommunications  or  broadband,  water, 

or sewer, for nonpayment; or 

(F)  threaten  to  take  any  of  the  foregoing 

actions. 

(2)  RULE OF CONSTRUCTION.Nothing  in 

this  section  may  be  construed  to  prohibit  a  small 

business  or  nonprofit  organization  from  voluntarily 

paying, in whole or in part, a debt. 

