(A) DEPOSITORY INSTITUTIONS.A depos-

itory  institution  that  has  a  legal  interest  in  the 

collateral  for  a  loan  or  another  financial  service 

provided  to  an  owner,  employee,  or  operator  of 

a cannabis-related legitimate business or service 

provider,  or  to  an  owner  or  operator  of  real  es-

tate  or  equipment  that  is  leased  or  sold  to  a 

cannabis-related  legitimate  business  or  service 

provider,  shall  not  be  subject  to  criminal,  civil, 

or  administrative  forfeiture  of  that  legal  inter-

est  pursuant  to  any  Federal  law  for  providing 

such loan or other financial service. 

(B)  FEDERAL RESERVE BANKS AND FED-

ERAL HOME LOAN BANKS.A  Federal  reserve 

bank  or  Federal  Home  Loan  Bank  that  has  a 

legal  interest  in  the  collateral  for  a  loan  or  an-

other  financial  service  provided  to  a  depository 

institution  that  provides  a  financial  service  to  a 

cannabis-related  legitimate  business  or  service 

provider,  or  to  an  owner  or  operator  of  real  es-

tate  or  equipment  that  is  leased  or  sold  to  a 

cannabis-related  legitimate  business  or  service 

provider,  shall  not  be  subject  to  criminal,  civil, 

or  administrative  forfeiture  of  that  legal  inter-

