(5)  DEPOSITORY INSTITUTION.The  term  de-

pository institution means 

(A)  a  depository  institution  as  defined  in 

section  3(c)  of  the  Federal  Deposit  Insurance 

Act (12 U.S.C. 1813(c)); 

(B)  a  Federal  credit  union  as  defined  in 

