(10)  INSURER.The  term  insurer  has  the 

meaning  given  that  term  under  section  313(r)  of 

title 31, United States Code. 

(11)  MANUFACTURER.The  term  manufac-

turer  means  a  person  who  manufactures,  com-

pounds,  converts,  processes,  prepares,  or  packages 

cannabis or cannabis products. 

(12)  PRODUCER.The  term  producer  means 

a  person  who  plants,  cultivates,  harvests,  or  in  any 

way facilitates the natural growth of cannabis. 

