(6) USE OF FUNDS. 

(A)  IN GENERAL.During  the  covered  pe-

riod,  an  eligible  entity  that  receives  a  grant 

under  this  subsection  may  use  the  grant  funds 

for 

(i) payroll costs; 

(ii)  payments  of  principal  or  interest 

on any mortgage obligation; 

(iii)  rent  payments, 

including  rent 

under a lease agreement; 

(iv) utilities; 

(v)  maintenance,  including  construc-

tion to accommodate outdoor seating; 

(vi) 

supplies, 

including  protective 

equipment and cleaning materials; 

(vii)  food,  beverage,  and  operational 

expenses  that  are  within  the  scope  of  the 

normal  business  practice  of  the  eligible  en-

tity before the covered period; 

(viii) debt obligations to suppliers that 

were incurred before the covered period; 

