NORITY BUSINESS ENTERPRISES.If  the  Ad-

ministrator  determines  that  a  particular  Amer-

ican Indian, Alaska Native, or Native Hawaiian 

community  does  not  receive  sufficient  grant 

amounts  under  subsection  (c)  or  section  1108 

of  the  CARES  Act,  the  Administrator  shall 

carry  out  additional  outreach  directly  to  minor-

ity  business  enterprises  located  in  that  commu-

nity to provide guidance regarding Federal pro-

grams  that  are  available  to  provide  support  to 

minority business enterprises. 

