other enhancements, including those provided by this 

legislation, to enhance the effectiveness of the CDFI 

Fund,  especially  reforms  to  support  minority-owned 

and  minority  led  CDFIs  in  times  of  crisis  and  be-

yond. 

(5)  Congress  should  conduct  robust  and  ongo-

ing  oversight  of  the  Department  of  the  Treasury, 

CDFI  Fund,  Federal  prudential  regulators,  SBA, 

and  other  Federal  agencies  to  ensure  they  fulfill 

their  obligations  under  the  law  as  well  as  implement 

