(2)  ESTABLISHMENT.The  Secretary  of  the 

Treasury  shall  establish  a  Neighborhood  Capital  In-

vestment Program (the Program) to support the ef-

forts of low- and moderate-income community finan-

cial  institutions  to,  among  other  things,  provide 

