(B)  CONTINGENCY OF PAYMENTS BASED 

ON CERTAIN FINANCIAL CRITERIA. 

(i)  DEFERRAL.Any  annual  pay-

ments  under  this  subsection  shall  be  de-

ferred  in  any  quarter  or  payment  period  if 

any of the following is true: 

(I)  The  low-  and  moderate-in-

come  community  institution  fails  to 

meet  the  Tier  1  capital  ratio  or  simi-

lar  ratio  as  determined  by  the  Sec-

retary. 

(II)  The  low-  and  moderate-in-

come  community  financial  institution 

fails to achieve positive net income for 

the quarter or payment period. 

(III)  The  low-  and  moderate-in-

come  community  financial  institution 

determines that the payment would be 

detrimental  to  the  financial  health  of 

the institution. 

