(10)  TERMINATION OF INVESTMENT AUTHOR-

ITY.The  authority  to  make  capital  investments  in 

low- and moderate-income community financial insti-

tutions,  including  commitments  to  purchase  pre-

ferred  stock  or  other  instruments,  provided  under 

the  Program  shall  terminate  on  the  date  that  is  36 

months  after  the  date  of  enactment  of  this  sub-

section. 

