SEC.  706.  EMERGENCY  SUPPORT  FOR  CDFIS  AND  COMMU-

NITIES. 

(a) AUTHORIZATION OF APPROPRIATIONS.There is 

authorized to be appropriated to the Community Develop-

ment Financial Institutions Fund $2,000,000,000 for fis-

cal year 2021, for providing financial assistance and tech-

nical assistance under subparagraphs (A) and (B) of sec-

