4707(a)(1)),  except  that  subsections  (d)  and  (e)  of  such 

section 108 shall not apply to the provision of such assist-

ance,  for  the  Bank  Enterprise  Award  program,  and  for 

financial  assistance,  technical  assistance,  training,  and 

outreach  programs  designed  to  benefit  Native  American, 

Native  Hawaiian,  and  Alaska  Native  communities  and 

provided  primarily  through  qualified  community  develop-

ment  lender  organizations  with  experience  and  expertise 

