Code,  federally  insured  depository  institutions,  com-

munity  development  financial  institutions  and  State, 

local, or Tribal government entities. 

(5)  Since  its  founding,  the  CDFI  Fund  has 

awarded  over  $3,300,000,000  to  CDFIs  and  CDEs, 

allocated  $54,000,000,000 

in 

tax  credits,  and 

