SEC. 710. CDFI BOND GUARANTEE REFORM. 

Effective  October  1,  2020,  section  114A(e)(2)(B)  of 

the  Riegle  Community  Development  and  Regulatory  Im-

provement  Act  of  1994  (12  U.S.C.  4713a(e)(2)(B))  is 

