TITLE  IXSUPPORT  FOR  A  RO-
BUST  GLOBAL  RESPONSE  TO 
THE COVID19 PANDEMIC 

SEC. 901. UNITED STATES POLICIES. 

(a)  UNITED STATES POLICIES AT THE INTER-

NATIONAL FINANCIAL INSTITUTIONS. 

(1)  IN GENERAL.The  Secretary  of  the  Treas-

ury shall instruct the United States Executive Direc-

tor  at  each  international  financial  institution  (as  de-

fined  in  section  1701(c)(2)  of  the  International  Fi-

nancial  Institutions  Act  (22  U.S.C.  262r(c)(2)))  to 

