of registered voters in the State or other official 

record  or  other  document  used  by  the  State  to 

verify the signatures of voters unless 

(i)  at  least  2  election  officials  make 

the determination; and 

(ii)  each  official  who  makes  the  de-

termination  has  received  training  in  proce-

dures used to verify signatures. 

