any  ballot  submitted  by  an  individual  who  is  entitled  to 

vote by absentee ballot under the Uniformed and Overseas 

Citizens  Absentee  Voting  Act  (52  U.S.C.  20301  et  seq.). 

(j)  EFFECTIVE DATE.This  section  shall  apply 

with respect to the regularly scheduled general election for 

Federal office held in November 2020 and each succeeding 

election for Federal office. 

SEC. 323. ABSENTEE BALLOT TRACKING PROGRAM. 

(a)  REQUIREMENT.Each  State  shall  carry  out  a 

program to track and confirm the receipt of absentee bal-

lots in an election for Federal office under which the State 

or local election official responsible for the receipt of voted 

