SEC.  325.  COVERAGE  OF  COMMONWEALTH  OF  NORTHERN 

MARIANA ISLANDS. 

In  this  subtitle,  the  term  State  includes  the  Com-

monwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands. 

SEC.  326.  MINIMUM  REQUIREMENTS  FOR  EXPANDING 

ABILITY OF INDIVIDUALS TO VOTE. 

The  requirements  of  this  subtitle  are  minimum  re-

quirements, and nothing in this subtitle may be construed 

to prevent a State from establishing standards which pro-

mote the ability of individuals to vote in elections for Fed-

eral office, so long as such standards are not inconsistent 

with  the  requirements  of  this  subtitle  or  other  Federal 

laws.. 

(b)  CONFORMING AMENDMENT RELATING TO 

ISSUANCE OF VOLUNTARY GUIDANCE BY ELECTION AS-

SISTANCE COMMISSION.Section  311(b)  of  such  Act  (52 

U.S.C. 21101(b)) is amended 

(1)  by  striking  and  at  the  end  of  paragraph 

(2); 

(2)  by  striking  the  period  at  the  end  of  para-

graph (3) and inserting ; and; and 

(3)  by  adding  at  the  end  the  following  new 

paragraph: 

(4)  in  the  case  of  the  recommendations  with 

respect to subtitle C, June 30, 2020.. 

(c) ENFORCEMENT. 

