mination  and  Education  Assistance  Act  (25 

U.S.C. 5304). 

(E)  TRIBAL GOVERNMENT.The 

term 

Tribal  Government  means  the  recognized 

governing body of an Indian Tribe. 

(7) ENFORCEMENT. 

(A)  ATTORNEY GENERAL.The  Attorney 

General  may  bring  a  civil  action  in  an  appro-

priate  district  court  for  such  declaratory  or  in-

junctive  relief  as  is  necessary  to  carry  out  this 

subsection. 

