SEC. 111. COORDINATION. 

In implementing this title, the Secretary shall coordi-

nate with the Secretary of Transportation. 

SEC. 112. DIRECT APPROPRIATION. 

Notwithstanding  any  other  provision  of  law,  there  is 

appropriated,  out  of  amounts  in  the  Treasury  not  other-

wise appropriated, $28,300,000,000 to carry out this title. 

