(c)  CONSULTATION.When  developing  a  plan  under 

subsection (a), the Secretary of Transportation shall con-

sult with aviation industry and labor stakeholders, includ-

ing representatives of 

(1) air carriers; 

(2) small, medium, and large hub airports; 

(3) labor organizations that represent airline pi-

lots,  flight  attendants,  air  carrier  airport  customer 

