clusive  bargaining  representative  of  air  traffic  con-

trollers of the Federal Aviation Administration; 

(5)  the  labor  organization  certified  under  such 

section  as  the  exclusive  bargaining  representative  of 

airway  transportation  systems  specialists  and  avia-

tion  safety  inspectors  of  the  Federal  Aviation  Ad-

ministration; and 

(6)  such  other  stakeholders  as  the  Secretary 

considers appropriate. 

