of the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency 

Assistance Act (42 U.S.C. 5191(b)), and under any subse-

quent major disaster declaration under section 401 of such 

Act  (42  U.S.C.  5170)  that  supersedes  such  emergency 

declaration, shall be at a 100 percent Federal cost share. 

