food directly from food producers and farmers. 

(b)  APPLICATION TO SUBSEQUENT MAJOR DIS-

ASTER.The  activities  described  in  subsection  (a)  may 

also be eligible for assistance under any major disaster de-

clared by the President under section 401 of such Act (42 

U.S.C.  5170)  that  supersedes  the  emergency  declaration 

described in such subsection. 

