TITLE IACCOUNTABILITY 

SEC.  101.  CONGRESSIONAL  NOTIFICATION  OF  CHANGE  IN 

STATUS OF INSPECTOR GENERAL. 

(a) CHANGE IN STATUS OF INSPECTOR GENERAL OF 

OFFICES.Section  3(b)  of  the  Inspector  General  Act  of 

1978 (5 U.S.C. App.) is amended 

(1)  by  inserting  ,  is  placed  on  paid  or  unpaid 

non-duty status, after is removed from office; 

(2)  by  inserting  ,  change  in  status,  after 

any such removal; and 

(3) by inserting , change in status, after be-

fore the removal. 

(b) CHANGE IN STATUS OF INSPECTOR GENERAL OF 

DESIGNATED FEDERAL ENTITIES.Section  8G(e)(2)  of 

the  Inspector  General  Act  of  1978  (5  U.S.C.  App.)  is 

amended 

(1)  by  inserting  ,  is  placed  on  paid  or  unpaid 

non-duty status, after office; 

(2)  by  inserting  ,  change  in  status,  after 

any such removal; and 

(3) by inserting , change in status, after be-

fore the removal. 

