(1)  individuals  who  were  scheduled  for  an  in- 

person oath ceremony that was cancelled due to such 

public health emergency; 

(2) individuals who were provided written notice 

pursuant  to  subsection  (c)(1)  of  the  option  of  par-

ticipating in a remote oath ceremony; 

