(f)  ESSENTIAL CRITICAL INFRASTRUCTURE LABOR 

OR SERVICES.For purposes of this section, the term es-

sential  critical  infrastructure  labor  or  services  means 

labor  or  services  performed  in  an  essential  critical  infra-

structure  sector,  as  described  in  the  Advisory  Memo-

randum on Identification of Essential Critical Infrastruc-

ture  Workers  During  COVID19  Response,  revised  by 

the Department of Homeland Security on April 17, 2020. 

