(4) ADJUSTMENT IN WAIVER NUMBERS. 

(A) INCREASES. 

(i)  IN GENERAL.Except  as  pro-

vided  in  clause  (ii),  if  in  any  fiscal  year, 

not  less  than  90  percent  of  the  waivers 

provided  under  paragraph  (1)(B)  are  uti-

lized  by  States  receiving  at  least  5  such 

waivers,  the  number  of  such  waivers  allot-

ted  to  each  State  shall  increase  by  5  for 

each subsequent fiscal year. 

