reached during a given fiscal year referred to in 

such  subparagraph,  the  numerical  limitation 

specified in such subparagraph for the following 

fiscal year shall be increased by a number equal 

to the difference between 

(i)  the  numerical  limitation  specified 

in  subparagraph  (A)  for  the  given  fiscal 

year; and 

(ii) the number of principal aliens pro-

vided  special  immigrant  status  under  this 

subsection during the given fiscal year. 

