(c)  PERIOD DESCRIBED.The  period  described  in 

this subsection 

(1)  begins  on  the  first  day  of  the  public  health 

emergency  declared  by  the  Secretary  of  Health  and 

Human  Services  under  section  319  of  the  Public 

Health Service Act (42 U.S.C. 247d) with respect to 

COVID19; and 

(2)  ends  90  days  after  the  date  on  which  such 

public health emergency terminates. 

