family members; 

(7)  advance  policies  and  procedures  for  juve-

nile  delinquency  program  proceedings  (including 

court  proceedings)  and  probation  conditions  so  that 

in-person  reporting  requirements  for  juveniles  are 

replaced with virtual or telephonic appearances with-

out penalty; 

