TITLE IIIVICTIMS OF CRIME 

ACT AMENDMENTS 

SEC. 301. SHORT TITLE. 

This title may be cited as the Victims of Crime Act 

Fix Act of 2020. 

SEC. 302. DEPOSITS OF FUNDING INTO THE CRIME VICTIMS 

FUND. 

Section 1402(b) of the Victims of Crime Act of 1984 

(34 U.S.C. 20101(b)) is amended 

(1)  in  paragraph  (4),  by  striking  and  at  the 

end; 

(2)  in  paragraph  (5),  by  striking  the  period  at 

the end and inserting ; and; and 

(3) by adding at the end the following: 

(6)  any  funds  that  would  otherwise  be  depos-

ited  in  the  general  fund  of  the  Treasury  collected  as 

pursuant to 

(A)  a  deferred  prosecution  agreement;  or 

(B) a non-prosecution agreement.. 

