laration issued by the President on March 13, 2020, 

pursuant to section 501(b) of the Robert T. Stafford 

Disaster  Relief  and  Emergency  Assistance  Act  (42 

U.S.C.  5191(b)),  during  the  period  covered  by  such 

emergency  declaration  and  any  subsequent  major 

disaster  declaration  under  section  401  of  such  Act 

(42  U.S.C.  5170)  that  supersedes  such  emergency 

declaration. 

